title: The Wiggles: yummy yummy
creator_credit: Wiggles Touring Pty Ltd, Nick Pike and Chisholm McTavish
brief_description: Greg, Murray, Anthony and Jeff sing 14 of your favourite songs; “Hot potato”, “D.O.R.O.T.H.Y”, “Pufferbillies”, “Henry’s dance”, “Walk”, “Joannie works with one hammer”, “The Monkey dance”, “Crunchy munchy honey cakes”, “Shaky shaky”, “Teddy bear hug”, “Havena shalom alachem”, “I am a dancer”, “Numbers rhumba” and “Fruit salad”. There are special appearances from Captain Feathersword, Henry the Octopus, Wags the Dog and Dorothy the Dinosaur.
